react-router -- for redirecting to new page,allows changing the browser URL, and keeps the UI in sync with the URL.

uuid -- unique id generator package

react-hot-toast -- Library that aims to include toast notifications in your React applications easily and intuitively

react-avatar -- React avatar component makes it possible to generate avatars based on user information.

code-mirror -- code editor component for the web. It can be used in websites to implement a text input field 

express -- build server

socket -- build connection

nodemon -- for not manually restart server after changes in file

